          "_name": "features038",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features38\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\" checked>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>3</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Image</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"autoSize\" title=\"Auto Size\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Height\" name=\"imageHeight\" min=\"3\" max=\"6\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\" condition=\"autoSize\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Un dispositif pédagogique concret et adapté</b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Les interventions, d'une durée de 50 à 90 minutes, s'adressent aux élèves du CM2 au post-bac.<br><br>Elles ne relèvent ni du prosélytisme, ni du relativisme, mais s'inscrivent dans une laïcité ouverte, respectueuse de la liberté de conscience de chacun.<br><br>L'originalité du dispositif repose sur l'animation par un binôme mixte (un chrétien et un musulman), simples croyants venus partager leur expérience d’amitié.<br><br>La pédagogie est participative et s'appuie sur trois modules principaux :\n<br>• Le module « Choisir la Fraternité » : Axé sur l'écoute, le respect et la déconstruction des préjugés.<br>    • Le module « Pardon » : un temps de réflexion et de partage autour de la dynamique du pardon.\n<br>    • Le module « Marie » : Une réflexion sur Marie/Maryam comme modèle de foi et figure de paix commune à l'Évangile et au Coran.<br><br></p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Get started</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/gemini-generated-image-8sts2s8sts2s8sts-1165x1165.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row row-reverse justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 1\">\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Des garanties de sérieux et de qualité</b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Cette démarche bénéficie d'une large reconnaissance institutionnelle. Elle est validée par des partenaires de premier plan tels que la Fondation de l'Islam de France, la Grande Mosquée de Paris ou l'Archevêché de Marseille.<br><br>De plus, les animateurs reçoivent une formation solide conçue avec l’ISTR (Institut de Science et de Théologie des Religions) de l'Institut Catholique de Paris, garantissant la justesse des contenus abordés.<br><br>Ils en parlent...\n<br><br>L'impact sur les jeunes est immédiat, comme en témoigne cet élève de 1ère : « Merci d'avoir fait évoluer mon regard sur la religion et la fraternité ! »\n<br><br>Pour les chefs d'établissement, c'est un outil précieux pour former des « bâtisseurs de paix » capables de vivre sereinement dans un monde pluriel.<br></p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Get started</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/fraternitc3a920snap2020fais20voir20ton20soutien20120020x20120020px-1165x1165.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 2\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Contact et informations</b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Si vous souhaitez déployer ce projet au sein de vos classes ou de vos mouvements de jeunes, l'équipe nationale se tient à votre disposition pour adapter le format à vos besoins.\n<br><br>Contact : M. Jean-François de Marignan (Coordination nationale EAM)<br>\n<br>Téléphone&nbsp;<br> ➡️ 07 87 14 28 49\n<br><br>Email&nbsp;<br>➡️ classes@ensembleavecmarie.org\n<br><br>Site web&nbsp;<br>➡️ www.ensembleavecmarie.org<br></p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Get started</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/eam-960x960.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vf3T4YazCu",
          "_anchor": "features038-b9",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "footer1",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".social-row": {
              "display": "flex",
              "flex-wrap": "wrap"
            },
            ".soc-item": {
              "display": "flex",
              "align-items": "center",
              "justify-content": "center",
              "border-radius": "50%",
              "background-color": "white",
              "margin-right": "0.5rem",
              "margin-bottom": "1rem",
              "padding": "0.5rem",
              "height": "2.5rem",
              "width": "2.5rem"
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              ".row": {
                "text-align": "center"
              },
              ".social-row": {
                "justify-content": "center"
              }
            },
            ".list": {
              "list-style": "none",
              "padding-left": "0",
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "2rem"
              },
              "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
                "margin-bottom": "0rem"
              },
              "color": "#ffffff",
              "text-align": "justify"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#ffffff"
            },
            ".mbr-iconfont": {
              "color": "black"
            },
            ".list DIV": {
              "text-align": "justify"
            }
          },
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"footer1\" group=\"Footers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" global once=\"footers\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Social\" name=\"showSocial\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"socialCount\" title=\"Social Count\" min=\"1\" max=\"4\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"showSocial\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Copyright\" name=\"showCopyright\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#373365\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#373365\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n    \n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row mbr-white\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <h5 mbr-text class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Citation biblique</b></h5>\n                <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".list\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <div>« Si quelqu'un dit : \"J'aime Dieu\", alors qu'il a de la haine contre son frère, c'est un menteur. En effet, celui qui n'aime pas son frère, qu'il voit, est incapable d'aimer Dieu, qu'il ne voit pas. </div><div>Et voici le commandement que nous tenons de lui : celui qui aime Dieu, qu'il aime aussi son frère. » <span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">— <b>Première lettre de Jean 4, 20-21</b></span></div>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <h5 mbr-text class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Partenaires</b></h5>\n                <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".list\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <div><a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/content/romancuria/fr/dicasteri/dicastero-dialogo-interreligioso.index.html\" class=\"text-success text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">Vatican Dicastère</a></div><div><a href=\"https://relations-catholiques-musulmans.cef.fr/\" class=\"text-success\" target=\"_blank\">Conf. des évêques de France</a></div><div><a href=\"https://lille.catholique.fr/famille-societe/dialogue/dialogue-interreligieux-2/\" class=\"text-success\" target=\"_blank\">Diocèse de Lille</a></div>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 text-center\">\n                <style>\n                    .map-wrapper {\n                        filter: grayscale(100%);\n                        border-radius: 8px;\n                        overflow: hidden;\n                        display: inline-block;\n                    }\n                </style>\n                <div class=\"map-wrapper\">\n                    <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2530.021627962608!2d3.0880876763192586!3d50.64528947162996!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47c32a04413994e3%3A0x99509bf2778763a5!2s74%20Rue%20Hippolyte%20Lefebvre%2C%2059800%20Lille!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1773909007679!5m2!1sfr!2sfr\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><br><b>Maison Paul VI</b></h5>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                    Dialogue interreligieux<br><br>\n                    74 Rue Hippolyte Lefebvre<br>\n                    59800 Lille<br>\n                    03 20 06 43 02<br></p>\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle && showSocial\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><b>Social</b></h5>\n                <div class=\"social-row display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSocial\">\n                    <div class=\"soc-item\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/interreligieuxlille\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon-facebook socicon\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 51, 101); fill: rgb(55, 51, 101);\"></span>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>1\">\n                        <a href=\"https://x.com/InterLille\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon-twitter socicon\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 51, 101); fill: rgb(55, 51, 101);\"></span>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>2\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sdrmlille/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon-instagram socicon\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 51, 101); fill: rgb(55, 51, 101);\"></span>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"soc-item\" mbr-if=\"socialCount>3\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@sdrmlille\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont socicon-tiktok socicon\" style=\"color: rgb(55, 51, 101); fill: rgb(55, 51, 101);\"></span>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 mt-4\" mbr-if=\"showCopyright\">\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mb-0 mbr-fonts-style copyright align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".copyright\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">© 2026 Diocèse de Lille. Tous droits réservés.&nbsp;<a href=\"mentions.html\" class=\"text-success text-primary\">Mentions Légales</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vf3RSrWLBx",
